                        boolean Sensitive,
                        boolean WholeWord,
                        boolean Highlight,
                        boolean SearchInAllPages)
Set the global search criteria. You must call TTrace.winTrace().findNext() to position to the next or previous matching node

Parameters:
Text - Text to search
Sensitive - Search is case sensitive
WholeWord - Match only whole word
Highlight - Highlight results
SearchInAllPages - Call to FindNext will search also in other traces windows if true
